n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Echoes Network</h1>\n        <p>Where stories resonate and ideas take flight.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Featured Podcasts</h2>\n        <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x150/1f3a93/ffffff?text=Podcast+1\" alt=\"Podcast 1 Cover\">\n                <h3>The Infinite Loop</h3>\n                <p>Exploring the cutting edge of technology and its impact on society.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x150/2e59a0/ffffff?text=Podcast+2\" alt=\"Podcast 2 Cover\">\n                <h3>Chronicles of the Past</h3>\n                <p>Unearthing forgotten histories and bringing the past to life.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x150/0077b6/ffffff?text=Podcast+3\" alt=\"Podcast 3 Cover\">\n                <h3>Whispers of the Cosmos</h3>\n                <p>Journeying through the mysteries of space and the universe.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x150/1f3a93/ffffff?text=Podcast+4\" alt=\"Podcast 4 Cover\">\n                <h3>Mindful Musings</h3>\n                <p>In-depth conversations on mental well-being and personal growth.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Echoes Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}